oncepts are explained  but rigorous proofs are omitted  Numerous examples are provided to illuminate new ideas and provide practice  Each section ends with exercises  with answers to odd questions appearing in the back  The text is currently in use by Cadets of the Virginia Military Institute  and is appropriate for undergraduates in mathematics and the sciences  as well as advanced high school students  Click here to download Fundamentals of Matrix Algebra in pdf format  Click here to purchase a paperback copy of the text from Amazon com  Lt  Col  Gregory Hartman Home Resources VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 